Interface GettersAndSettersFactory.Instantiator<T>

Type Parameters:
T - any class to allocate memory for
Enclosing class:
GettersAndSettersFactory
public static interface GettersAndSettersFactory.Instantiator<T>

This interface can be used as a type of variable to store any instantiator.
